snippet.title: Guns Girl - Mysterious Deep 5.4 Version PV
snippet.description:
New version PV of Guns Girl:
·New Event: 
"Mysterious Deep" -- The secret of the world lies in the Galan blue, where the two sides gather.
"Aurora Matrix" --Brave duo explore mysterious tech relics!
"Molten Maze" -- Scattered belongings around the volcano have raised new hopes.Traveler, are you really still alive?
·New Equipment
·Additional stability improvements and bug fixes
